OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FThis should be the first port of call
OL,7,Fif you are struggling to keep up with
OL,8,Fpayments, as water companies are often
OL,9,Fable to adapt your payment plan and
OL,10,Fprovide advice on how to keep costs
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,13,FThere are schemes in place to help
OL,14,Fpeople with their water bills,
OL,15,Fincluding WaterSure. This scheme is
OL,16,Favailable to anybody on benefits and
OL,17,Fthose who use a lot of water for
OL,18,Fmedical reasons or because the
OL,19,Fhousehold has three or more school-age
OL,20,Fchildren in full-time education.
