OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FYou should get in contact with your
OL,7,Flocal water provider to find out what
OL,8,Fprogrammes might be in place to help.
OL,9,FYou can find out who supplies your
OL,10,Fwater on the Consumer Council for
OL,11,FWater (CCW) .
OL,13,FConsider a water meter
OL,15,FIn England and Wales you are billed
OL,16,Ffor water either through companies
OL,17,Festimating how much water you use
OL,18,Fbased on the size of the property, or
OL,19,Fby paying for the exact amount you
OL,20,Fuse, measured by a water meter.
