OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FAll homes built since 1990 should have
OL,7,Fa water meter, and if not you can get
OL,8,Fone installed for free.
OL,10,FThe CCW to calculate whether you would
OL,11,Fbenefit from having a water meter
OL,12,Finstalled, and your water company
OL,13,Fshould also be able to let you know
OL,14,Fwhether it is worth getting a meter.
OL,16,FIn Scotland water bills are based on
OL,17,Fcouncil tax bands, while there are no
OL,18,Fdomestic charges for water in Northern
OL,19,FIreland.
