OL,3,CWhat should you do if you're
OL,4,Cstruggling to pay your water bill?
OL,6,FIt is always best to speak to your
OL,7,Fprovider if you are having trouble
OL,8,Fpaying your bills to negotiate an
OL,9,Falternative payment plan than
OL,10,Fknowingly not paying for your water.
OL,12,FIf you do leave a water bill unpaid,
OL,13,Fyour provider will send one or more
OL,14,Freminder notices, with a final notice
OL,15,Fgiving you seven days to pay.
OL,17,FThe company may phone you to ask for
OL,18,Fpayment, or they could pass your debt
OL,19,Fonto a debt recovery agent.
